 use\nfacts about the `cramer` map.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L184-L186","name":"Matrix.cramer_reindex","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_reindex","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L177-L181","name":"Matrix.cramer_submatrix_equiv","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_submatrix_equiv","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L164-L174","name":"Matrix.sum_cramer_apply","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.sum_cramer_apply","doc":"Use linearity of `cramer` and vector evaluation to take `cramer A _ i` out of a summation. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L158-L160","name":"Matrix.sum_cramer","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.sum_cramer","doc":"Use linearity of `cramer` to take it out of a summation. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L149-L154","name":"Matrix.cramer_zero","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_zero","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L145-L146","name":"Matrix.cramer_subsingleton_apply","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_subsingleton_apply","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L139-L141","name":"Matrix.cramer_smul","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_smul","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L130-L136","name":"Matrix.cramer_one","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_one","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L123-L126","name":"Matrix.cramer_row_self","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_row_self","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L110-L120","name":"Matrix.cramer_transpose_row_self","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_transpose_row_self","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L106-L107","name":"Matrix.cramer_transpose_apply","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_transpose_apply","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L102-L103","name":"Matrix.cramer_apply","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_apply","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L98-L99","name":"Matrix.cramer","kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer","doc":"`cramer A b i` is the determinant of the matrix `A` with column `i` replaced with `b`,\nand thus `cramer A b` is the vector output by Cramer's rule on `A` and `b`.\n\nIf `A ⬝ x = b` has a unique solution in `x`, `cramer A` sends the vector `b` to `A.det • x`.\nOtherwise, the outcome of `cramer` is well-defined but not necessarily useful.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L86-L89","name":"Matrix.cramer_is_linear","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramer_is_linear","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L81-L83","name":"Matrix.cramerMap_is_linear","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramerMap_is_linear","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.lean#L77-L78","name":"Matrix.cramerMap","kind":"def","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Matrix/Adjugate.html#Matrix.cramerMap","doc":"`cramerMap A b i` is the determinant of the matrix `A` with column `i` replaced with `b`,\nand thus `cramerMap A b` is the vector output by Cramer's rule on `A` and `b`.\n\nIf `A ⬝ x = b` has a unique solution in `x`, `cramerMap A` sends the vector `b` to `A.det • x`.\nOtherwise, the outcome of `cramerMap` is well-defined but not necessarily useful.\n"}]}